safety equipment for the welding, construction and general
industrial markets. The company was acquired by Haas and
Mills last October for $67 million. Donaldson, Lufkin &amp;
Jenrette Securities Corp. provided the bridge loan for the
acquisition which is being replaced by the permanent
financing.
