million, makes combines and distributes farm implements and
tractors. Before 1985, it was part of Allis Chalmers Corp.
Klockner-Humboldt-Deutz is an industrial machinery company.
   Hamilton Robinson manages a $40 million fund for
management buy-outs and other investments.
